input:=["","","","",""];
pad:=[];
for y in [2..-2 by -1] do
	for x in [-2..2] do
		if Abs(x)+Abs(y) le 2 then
			Append(~pad,[x,y]);
		end if;
	end for;
end for;
keys:=["1","2","3","4","5","6","7","8","9","A","B","C","D"];
coord:=[0,0];
code:="";
for string in input do
	for n in [1..#string] do
		backup:=coord;
		case string[n]:
			when "U":
				coord[2]+:=1;
			when "D":
				coord[2]-:=1;
			when "R":
				coord[1]+:=1;
			when "L":
				coord[1]-:=1;
		end case;
		if not(coord in pad) then
			coord:=backup;
		end if;
	end for;
	code*:=keys[Index(pad,coord)];
end for;
code;
